  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pick the <strong>coriander</strong> leaves from their stalks&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Chop the stalks finely, keep the leaves separate&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>beef mince</strong>, <strong>fish sauce</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong><strong> garlic</strong> and <strong>coriander stalks</strong> (reserve the leaves for later!) to a medium bowl&nbsp;and mix thoroughly until combined (use clean hands!)</p>\r\n<p>Divide the beef mixture into 10 <span class=\"text-danger\">[20]</span> and shape into <strong>meatballs</strong></p>\r\n<p>Refrigerate the mixture until later&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <strong>carrot</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span>, then continue&nbsp;to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot 'ribbons'</p>\r\n<p>Slice the <strong>cucumber&nbsp;</strong>into rounds, then slice the disks into matchsticks&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Shred the<strong> little gem lettuce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid, with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the chilled <strong>meatballs</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cover with a lid and cook for 4-6 min, shaking occasionally so that the <strong>meatballs</strong> cook evenly</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/869.-step-4-x200.jpg",
